oar freely in the skies of Seikyu as the Crow Tengu, dive deep for sunken treasure as a slime, or till the ground of your farm as a boar. You’ll unlock even more Yokai forms on your journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/754b3a93c47522e78809a65a6b1fb722.avif?t=1770235873\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/aeef0da738ad8429b953ce6bf38c40e5.webp?t=1770235873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/aeef0da738ad8429b953ce6bf38c40e5.poster.webp?t=1770235873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=220 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate crops, craft furniture, and cook meals from locally sourced ingredients. Decorate your ancestral inn to reflect your unique vision - whether you're a fan of the cozy cottage aesthetic or traditional Eastern vibes, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Seikyu ranch will also be opening soon in a future content update! Raise livestock and collect ingredients to expand your resources!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/90c1398d10d1c6b59278e33235d9fd21.avif?t=1770235873\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/10af0e49c7bdadffad35ac5ee1146202.webp?t=1770235873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340520/extras/10af0e49c7bdadffad35ac5ee1146202.poster.webp?t=1770235873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=220 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the land’s seasonal changes, help the townsfolk with quests, and take part in various festivals and mini-games! You’ll soon feel part of this magical community.</p>",
